lems with class balancing there is, and I think its a serious thorn in SOE's side. Its too late to remove them and that's why SOE is trying something new(mitigating). If you look at the spell line up for EQOA for the PS2 you will notice that such spells(haste or slow) do not exist for any class/race. It will be 10 times easier to balance races/classes without these spells as well as NPC encounters. I have a strong feeling that EQ2 will not include haste and slow as well and that will be a good thing.<br>
