<br>
Technically nothing, but haste has a big impact on a NPC encounter because it significantly increases the DPS of the PC. The developers and designers had to plan and balance NPC encounters on both a PC with haste and a PC without haste. If they knew no PC would have haste the could get the encounter a lot closer to &quot;fair&quot;. If everyone had haste, they could adjust the encounter that way, if no one had haste they could adjust it that way too, but since they have to try to make a &quot;best guess on a middle ground&quot; we end up with the current balance of EQ. Hence Beastlords can solo in higher tier planes and mages can not, even though mage pets are superior in melee capabilites.<br>
<br>
